{"tid":1023715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受沙漠螞蟻啟發，科學家開發出不需 GPS 便可導航回家的步行機器人","createTime":"2019-02-16T04:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T05:43:24.000Z","uid":13468,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e1c6e4407322a203258a6402e2571e26c5b88f","tid":1023715,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:10:09.000Z","msg":"受沙漠螞蟻啟發，科學家開發出不需 GPS 便可導航回家的步行機器人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ddgbWEhBdIQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DddgbWEhBdIQ%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qn4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=90a4f8f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ddgbWEhBdIQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n受沙漠螞蟻的啟發，法國國家科學研究中心（CNRS）和艾克斯馬賽大學（AMU）團隊設計出第一個不須 GPS 就可隨機探索環境並自己返家的機器人「AntBot」，這項工作為自駕車和機器人技術導航開闢了新戰略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人眼對偏振光（polarized light）和紫外線輻射不敏感，但對名為 Cataglyphis 的沙漠螞蟻來說，這些光線正好可用來定位自己在哪裡，並找到返家的路。<br />\n<br />\n由於沙漠環境的炎熱使動物無法用費洛蒙標註，Cataglyphis 為了確保出外尋找食物後回程不會迷路，牠們會使用天空的偏振光透過簡單的計算步驟來測量航向，再運用眼睛對太陽運動速度的光學測量來確認距離。<br />\n<br />\n透過這種稱為路徑整合（path integration）的過程，將距離和航向兩個基本資訊結合，沒有費洛蒙的協助，Cataglyphis 外出尋找食物後也能順利返回巢穴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了讓 AntBot 有相同能耐，團隊配置了一個光學羅盤來透過偏振光確定航向，並透過指向太陽的光學運動感測器來測量涵蓋的距離。有了這些資訊，AntBot 證明能像沙漠螞蟻一樣探索環境並返回基地，在 14 公尺的涵蓋距離中精確到 1 公分。<br />\n<br />\nAntBot 的重量只有 2.3 公斤，有 6 英尺高的移動性，可在複雜環境移動，像是災區、崎嶇地形或探索外星土壤等，而這些地方正好輪式機器人和無人機難以運用。<br />\n<br />\n在類似螞蟻遇到的光照條件下，AntBot 整個歸巢軌跡記錄的誤差小至 0.67%，研究團隊認為，這種極簡感測器做到的導航精確度證明，生物啟發機器人技術有巨大的創新能力，未來或許有機會探索其他領域的潛在應用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/02/15/antbot-can-navigates-like-an-ant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F02%2F15%2Fantbot-can-navigates-like-an-ant%2F&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qn4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=279fbaff\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/02/15/antbot-can-navigates-like-an-ant/</a>"},{"pid":"13a7378bd13269eb2a94e3234dbd4ef2d253cab2","tid":1023715,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"無光個時就用GPS?"},{"pid":"0dbd83d0f7f02aa998a29ec1638819c5bb766577","tid":1023715,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"咁落雨點算"},{"pid":"d09e0edd826eae78e193888f726d6698a0ce0751","tid":1023715,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"13a7378bd13269eb2a94e3234dbd4ef2d253cab2","tid":1023715,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"無光個時就用GPS?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"用電筒照咪有光<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a0d234a108fddba49c4fdf4b16304220471555","tid":1023715,"uid":156203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"螞蟻都識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5b5b8a1ffd6699671891564b8d3abcc6d42f0e","tid":1023715,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83ae06ffa159da54704ebc745b6a1b043c4270a8","tid":1023715,"uid":88263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shh0S7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shh0S7.png&h=dfff3e6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e51efd6ea400b29bd6b00550f5eb40f34482ee0","tid":1023715,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以從頭講多次呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bb424414ac6f5b494e1fda80fdf67fc8c2a5eb","tid":1023715,"uid":46408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:43:24.000Z","msg":"唔知可唔可以用係火星探索呢"}]}